{"tid":1296443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將警察通例第20章第20-14節,印TEE 或BANNER,有冇得諗?","createTime":"2019-07-08T11:19:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T11:35:51.000Z","uid":86840,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fbf68d740a4ef860dca88eed5777bf095a87cc5c","tid":1296443,"uid":86840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:19:45.000Z","msg":"下次散步/野餐,係唔係應該印呢段野大字報當BANNER用?<br />\n或者印TEE 有冇得諗?印TEE就 撚靚 下D TYPO<br />\n<br />\n警察通例第20章第20-14節第2點列明：<br />\n<br />\n只要外進行的工作不妨礙妥人員為保管委任證， 警務人員在任何時候均需隨身攜帶委任證。<br />\n<br />\n便衣人員不論是否當值，在與市民接觸或行駛警察權時，必須表明身份及出示委任證。<br />\n<br />\n在案發現場的便衣人員，須將委任證掛在顯眼的地方，讓人便於辨認其身份。"},{"pid":"ef7c7a91984bb47b6e95bf7ec6163786cb1b4334","tid":1296443,"uid":86840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:21:14.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"3790b845d64cd3fa99c3bf13f3402f40c6c23f46","tid":1296443,"uid":194298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:22:04.000Z","msg":"唔好哂錢，偉人都知佢地違規，佢地自己都知"},{"pid":"c218335a6b366cb7aba262c4a789ed26d92ac7b6","tid":1296443,"uid":181033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:24:23.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\nPrint一疊A4出來派前線<br />\n一人一張撻警犬會唔會性價比好D"},{"pid":"39048e72ec6a3ff6c51bcda12eb1ea27f726bc8f","tid":1296443,"uid":86840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:25:20.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">[member]而家真係有任何野都阻止唔到呢班畜牲[/member]</code></pre>"},{"pid":"8d0511a8e102b69737ea6556382081f274949f5e","tid":1296443,"uid":86840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c218335a6b366cb7aba262c4a789ed26d92ac7b6","tid":1296443,"uid":181033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:24:23.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\nPrint一疊A4出來派前線<br />\n一人一張撻警犬會唔會性價比好D"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:26:21.000Z","msg":"我諗拉BANNER應該最平,同睇得清楚"},{"pid":"224acc3294c961e4572c08381594ea053eac595e","tid":1296443,"uid":74561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1